#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:2
msgid "整板检测"
msgstr "Whole Board Inspection"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:4
msgid "**此页面的用途**"
msgstr "**What this page covers**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:6
msgid ""
"针对 PCB **整体表面** "
"的检测（不依赖具体元件）。常用于检测元件之间、丝印边缘等区域的污渍、异物、残留物等表面缺陷，作为对单元件检测的补充。整板检测的 ROI "
"不再以单个元件为单位，而是以 **包含 / 排除区域** 为单位划定。"
msgstr ""
"Inspects the **entire PCB surface** without relying on individual "
"components. Useful for surface defects in regions between components or "
"along silkscreen edges — contamination, foreign objects, residue, and so on "
"— as a complement to per-component inspection. The ROI is defined in terms "
"of **Include / Exclude Regions** rather than individual components."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:8
msgid "**如何进入**"
msgstr "**How to open it**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:10
msgid "进入 **产品编程页面**（Teach），点击顶部标签页 **整板检测**。"
msgstr ""
"Open the **Teach** page for a product, then click the **Whole Board "
"Inspection** tab at the top."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:-1
msgid "整板检测主界面：左侧检测项列表 + 包含 / 排除区域工具 + 中央 PCB 画布"
msgstr ""
"Whole Board Inspection main view: inspection-item list on the left, "
"Include/Exclude region tools, and the PCB canvas in the center."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:16
msgid "**操作流程**"
msgstr "**Workflow**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:18
msgid "**1. 启用检测项**"
msgstr "**1. Enable inspection items**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:20
msgid "页面右侧提供检测项列表。当前支持的检测项："
msgstr ""
"The right side of the page lists the available inspection items. Currently "
"supported:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:22
msgid ""
"**表面污染检测（Surface Contamination）**：基于 AI 模型，识别 PCB "
"表面的污渍、油渍、毛刺、异物等污染缺陷。每个检测项可独立启用 / 关闭。"
msgstr ""
"**Surface Contamination**: an AI-driven check that flags stains, oil, burrs,"
" and foreign objects on the PCB surface. Each inspection item can be enabled"
" or disabled independently."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:24
msgid "需要时勾选对应检测项的开关。"
msgstr "Toggle the switch on each inspection item as needed."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:26
msgid "**2. 绘制检测区域**"
msgstr "**2. Draw inspection regions**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:28
msgid "整板检测使用两类区域定义有效检测范围："
msgstr ""
"Whole Board Inspection uses two types of regions to define the effective "
"inspection area:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:30
msgid ""
"**包含区域（Include Regions，绿色）**：明确要检测的区域。若 **未定义任何包含区域**，系统默认将整块 PCB 作为检测范围。"
msgstr ""
"**Include Regions (green)**: areas explicitly marked for inspection. If **no"
" Include Region is defined**, the entire PCB is inspected by default."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:31
msgid ""
"**排除区域（Exclude "
"Regions，红色）**：在检测范围内主动排除的区域。常用于跳过治具边缘、丝印商标、二维码贴纸等不希望被误判为污渍的位置。"
msgstr ""
"**Exclude Regions (red)**: areas to skip within the inspection scope. "
"Commonly used to leave out fixture edges, silkscreen logos, barcode "
"stickers, and other patterns that would otherwise be mistaken for "
"contamination."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:33
msgid "在画布上点击工具栏对应按钮即可开始绘制："
msgstr "Click the matching toolbar button to start drawing on the canvas:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:35
msgid "选中绿色 **添加包含区域** 按钮 → 在画布上拖动框选包含区域。"
msgstr ""
"Click the green **Add Include Region** button, then drag on the canvas to "
"draw the region."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:36
msgid "选中红色 **添加排除区域** 按钮 → 在画布上拖动框选排除区域。"
msgstr ""
"Click the red **Add Exclude Region** button, then drag on the canvas to draw"
" the region."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:38
msgid "每个区域绘制完成后会出现在右侧的 **区域列表** 中。点击列表项可："
msgstr ""
"Each region appears in the **Region List** on the right after drawing. From "
"a list entry you can:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:40
msgid "**定位（Locate）**：让相机移动到该区域，便于核对位置。"
msgstr ""
"**Locate**: move the camera to the region so you can verify its position."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:41
msgid "**删除**：移除该区域。"
msgstr "**Delete**: remove the region."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:43
msgid "**3. 保存配置**"
msgstr "**3. Save the configuration**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:45
msgid "所有改动会自动保存到当前产品的整板检测配置中，无需手动点击保存按钮。检测时系统会自动按当前配置执行。"
msgstr ""
"Changes are saved to the product's Whole Board Inspection configuration "
"automatically; there is no manual save button. The runtime applies the "
"current configuration on every inspection."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:47
msgid "**表面污染检测（Surface Contamination）**"
msgstr "**Surface Contamination**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:49
msgid "表面污染检测以 AI 模型为核心。开启该检测项后："
msgstr ""
"Surface Contamination is driven by an AI model. With the item enabled:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:51
msgid "系统在每次检测时会对所有 **包含区域 - 排除区域** 内的像素做表面缺陷推理；"
msgstr ""
"On every inspection the system runs surface-defect inference over pixels "
"inside the **Include Regions minus the Exclude Regions**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:52
msgid "AI 给出的污染区域会在复检页面上以高亮显示，便于人工确认；"
msgstr ""
"The AI's flagged areas are highlighted on the review page for operator "
"confirmation."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:53
msgid "模型的可检范围会随产品配置与训练数据迭代而调整。"
msgstr ""
"The detectable defect categories shift over time as the product "
"configuration and training data evolve."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:55
msgid "**注意事项**"
msgstr "**Notes**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:59
msgid ""
"整板检测与单元件检测 **同时启用、各自独立判定**。整板检测发现的污染区域不会改变单元件的 OK/NG 状态，但在复检页面上会与元件 NG "
"一并列出，便于操作员同时处理。"
msgstr ""
"Whole Board Inspection and per-component inspection **both run at once, with"
" independent verdicts**. A contamination flagged by Whole Board Inspection "
"does not change any component's OK/NG status, but it is listed alongside the"
" component NGs on the review page so the operator can address both together."

